downloadTitle: Microsoft Dynamics AX 2009 SP1 White Paper: Country-Specific Update for Norway - EHF Electronic Invoicing
downloadDescription: This white paper describes the country-specific update released for Norway in rollup 8 for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2009 SP1. See Microsoft Knowledge Base article 2677618 for hotfix download information.

detailsSection: For more information about other features that apply to Norway, refer to the Help. Information that is specific to Norway includes (NOR) in the title.
